CardType ..> GameType
Deck --> GameType
Deck --> Instantiator
Deck ..> Card
Deck ..> Random
Deck ..> CardType
Game --> Deck
Game --> GameType
Game --> Player
Game ..> Random
Game ..> Card
Game ..> CardType
Player --> Card
Player ..> Random
Player ..> Instantiator
Player ..> CardType
GameUI --> Game
GameUI ..> ResourceBundle
GameUI ..> Player
GameUI ..> Card
GameUI ..> CardType
GameUI ..> GameType
Main ..> Game
Main ..> GameUI
Main ..> Deck
Main ..> Player
Main ..> Instantiator
Main ..> Card
Main ..> CardType
Main ..> GameType
Main ..> SecureRandom
Main ..> ArrayList
Instantiator ..> Card
Instantiator ..> CardType
Instantiator ..> Random
Instantiator ..> ArrayList

' New refactored relationships for card system
AttackCard ..|> PlayableCard
NopeCard ..|> PlayableCard
ShuffleCard ..|> PlayableCard
ExplodingKittenCard ..|> PlayableCard

