AttackCard ..> CardType
AttackCard ..> Player
NopeCard ..> CardType
ShuffleCard ..> CardType
ShuffleCard ..> Deck
ExplodingKittenCard ..> CardType
ExplodingKittenCard ..> Player

CardEffect --> List
CardEffect --> Map

GameContext --> Game
GameContext --> Player
GameContext --> Deck
GameContext --> GameUIHandler

CardFactory ..> PlayableCard
CardFactory ..> CardType
CardFactory ..> Supplier
CardFactory ..> Map

NopeHandler --> Game
NopeHandler --> GameUIHandler
NopeHandler ..> PlayableCard
NopeHandler ..> Player

CardValidator ..> PlayableCard
CardValidator ..> GameContext
CardValidator ..> Player
CardValidator ..> CardType

